Jenni Evans, News24Johannesburg -&nbsp;Two men were killed in a three-truck crash near Loskop Dam in Mpumalanga on Friday, paramedics said. One of the trucks lay on its side across the road and the others were lying in pieces in the ditch next to the road, ER24 spokesperson Russel Meiring said. The men were declared dead on the scene, and a man and a woman were treated on the scene and taken to hospital for follow-up care. Local authorities would investigate to establish the cause of the crash. Two men were killed in the crash near Loskop Dam (Supplied by ER24) Two men were killed in the crash near Loskop Dam (Supplied by ER24) 24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.